As soon as I heard
the island wasn't radioactive,

631
00:46:21,782 --> 00:46:25,386
I talked my way onto one of
the first choppers down here.

632
00:46:33,762 --> 00:46:35,496
Found them in the house.

633
00:46:37,464 --> 00:46:38,932
